data.description: Want to walk around the corner to Carl's?  Character, charm and close to everything is 2101 Fall Hill.   Walk to downtown or the canal path in moments.  Good size bedrooms with upper rooms having window seats with storage. The kitchen is updated and a yard that is private & fully fenced but a size that is easy to maintain.  Off street parking but plenty of on street for guests.  The basement has storage space.  HVAC replaced in 2017, new refrigerator in 2022. VRE is 5 minute drive or 30 minute walk.  I95 is 7 minutes away.  This haven is in an appealing part of downtown Fredericksburg you will love.
